　　華　　民　　國　 110　　年　　8 　　月　　16　　日\r\n                              書  記  官  許靜萍","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/110%2c%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%2c760%2c20210928%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,110,交易,760,20210928,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"交易","JNO":"760","JDATE":"20210928","JTITLE":"公共危險"}